  "description": "The Far East, 2071.<br>\nThe domain of the mad gods.<br>\n<br>\nIn the early 2050s, unknown life forms called “Oracle cells” begin their uncontrolled consumption of all life on Earth.<br>\nTheir ravenous appetite and remarkable adaptability earn them first dread, then awe, and finally the name “aragami”.<br>\nIn the face of an enemy completely immune to conventional weapons, urban civilization collapses, and each day humanity is driven further and further toward extinction.<br>\n<br>\nOne single ray of hope remains for humanity.<br>\nFollowing the development of “God Arcs”—living weapons which incorporate Oracle cells—their wielders are organized into an elite force.<br>\nIn a world ravaged by mad gods, these “God Eaters” fight a desperate war...<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Daisuki)",
